sub_title: Verbinder, bruggenbouwer, strateeg, regisseur van samenwerkingsverbanden en 				netwerken in het domein van welzijn en zorg.
summary:
Temporary crisis/change leader redesigning Business Processes. Applies different kinds of interventions depending on the stage of the Change; initiates visions and strategies as well as supports the implementation of business processes.

Starts from the knowledge, skills and competences of the respective client.

Core competences: visionary, strategic, emphatic, organizational skills, people manager, motivating and empowering people, independent, incorruptible, committed and determined.

Specialties: Change management (organizational, BPR and cultural).
Industries: public and professional services, police, governmental organizations etc.
